fr.upmc.components.examples.smoothing.sensor.interfaces

Interface SensorDataOfferedI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComponentImplementedI, DataOfferedI, OfferedI, java.rmi.Remote

    public interface SensorDataOfferedI
extends DataOfferedI
    The component interface SensorDataOfferedI defines a sensor provider service as a data exchanging API.

    Description

    The exchange of data uses the standard methods defined in the interfaces DataOfferedI.PullI and DataOfferedI.PushI, but the exchanged data will have to implement the interface SensorDataI defined here.
